{"id": "df1c3dbab2fccf206949ef2629bee846da2deb79f98049fea3f5b5c96a19975a", "item_id": "ed3012f531:0", "text": "RenderMan for Blender requires that RenderMan Pro Server also be installed and licensed."}
{"id": "deaea11df5a7e8d6c813a255f255a51c3afbed239c3815b339e6a4f7b5d016de", "item_id": "ed3012f531:1", "text": "For a list of supported Blender versions and instructions on installing RenderMan Pro Server, see"}
{"id": "31252854aa083990e214d562057184ca7c9b225cbecb4d815139fdb00379bb55", "item_id": "ed3012f531:4", "text": "RenderMan for Blender only supports the Intel version of Blender, as RenderMan does not yet support Apple Silicon."}
{"id": "37b345555d7ea6c1724d28076ce47b956d202574c211fefa36afba778f335373", "item_id": "ed3012f531:5", "text": "Downloading"}
{"id": "8f549a30daf6127b0c09d18094854050c0840dcad8ba45bcc85a4f76b10f4bad", "item_id": "ed3012f531:6", "text": "Non-commercial Users"}
{"id": "eb0aba35444e88f784e8e5078b72ee5462ae8cf308901db87615bda868456eeb", "item_id": "ed3012f531:7", "text": "Download the Non-Commercial RenderMan (NCR) installer:"}
{"id": "be1e5d26b9581ffbbe3f00d0640d9359508fbf7d3fe64346f3f9fd6a8d8690a8", "item_id": "ed3012f531:8", "text": "https://renderman.pixar.com/intro"}
{"id": "2349d6bb7ba2736fc1a03543377a0a25be4be3e5730ce1c8570bad234becbe15", "item_id": "ed3012f531:9", "text": "Run the installer, enter your forum username and password. Hit Next and an NCR license will be downloaded."}
{"id": "f41b83544fe784b7e34f62bc3364514ec0fb76bbe8c716098c31680be2c9aaab", "item_id": "ed3012f531:18", "text": "Next, make sure to select RenderMan Pro Server and RenderMan for Blender from the list and click Next. RenderMan Pro Server will then automatically install for you. For RenderMan for Blender, see the instructions below under the"}
{"id": "8749b1693f74941144464b73f49e322066f437079a400d0b11abffc6dffae2cc", "item_id": "ed3012f531:24", "text": "Installing"}
{"id": "1e54a9f638505a5f5067dfaf2421931c270a61bf21fecf1597c263b883a3298a", "item_id": "ed3012f531:20", "text": "section."}
{"id": "f538aecc7aedb32b01836d74d3ecf8282be1bd34efd563f957fa583db06a609d", "item_id": "ed3012f531:13", "text": "Commercial Users"}
{"id": "0e6008bd6ec91e6ca59d34fc21bb5855aebb022400130c0664796710bcff3e5b", "item_id": "ed3012f531:14", "text": "Visit the RenderMan downloads page:"}
{"id": "35ef0c0eefc450660c016d762d715217b3f83cb6cba312a7877281dd16bd157c", "item_id": "ed3012f531:15", "text": "https://renderman.pixar.com/forum/download.php"}
{"id": "6ac87acabaaf47ed92a649ad807bc4b6a4f3b55c9121224d136f6d40d8dc4191", "item_id": "ed3012f531:16", "text": "You can download the RenderMan Installer, for the platform you're running."}
{"id": "f5bb4b548cb34f80fc8aa03b85c9c04e0074a2581c07dca57069b52ae58129b1", "item_id": "ed3012f531:17", "text": "When you run the installer, it will ask you to input your forum username, password, and serial number."}
{"id": "f911e414cf6bdfc595532ab166b5ba0f63d73c021452fcdacbda363dda6ad8fb", "item_id": "ed3012f531:21", "text": "GitHub"}
{"id": "1eed69048274ab88d9e76cd28e287ab5d22cd20b63bdf3cd2e2e303b1a87a660", "item_id": "ed3012f531:22", "text": "If you are a developer, you can also clone RenderMan for Blender from the RenderMan GitHub repository:"}
{"id": "f6d4b0bccbd170295ff4e970dbeaf5024fade3d107fd29d830dff0122f5e50cb", "item_id": "ed3012f531:23", "text": "https://github.com/prman-pixar/RenderManForBlender"}
{"id": "5af249e5966a014e62de6aeca02dba3016f6eb84ff30033e603a0d5e668834e1", "item_id": "ed3012f531:25", "text": "Like any other addon for Blender, RenderMan for Blender can be installed from a .zip file in the Blender preferences, under the Addons tab:"}
{"id": "8fb10f06eb44469638d9fedce77560aa322d667520e8ad3123da06c1859d2b7f", "item_id": "ed3012f531:26", "text": "Click the Install button"}
{"id": "e8cf7def5884c765f2a20bfe26dd9af54537805b085f57abfe67652036e35e22", "item_id": "ed3012f531:27", "text": "Browse for the"}
{"id": "fa81ed03728bdda46fc55800c6e69bdda163fcc2b817a96a2a93d1b7e1080cc1", "item_id": "ed3012f531:28", "text": "RenderManForBlender_27.0_XXXXX.zip"}
{"id": "169050608e7fab592aa61370be6572b232d747ef53d4f545490be4dc1fcb65dc", "item_id": "ed3012f531:29", "text": "file. If you used the installers, the file should be in your Downloads folder."}
{"id": "b4440c49687f70341bc496f1e2a0092d585e8db5e28a481e35765ece585a25ca", "item_id": "ed3012f531:30", "text": "Click Install Add-On."}
{"id": "bdf7ebc5b5ae0eb6b7ecdb8878723dfac2813851ff66eab11e8a82e01b708d1c", "item_id": "ed3012f531:31", "text": "Now you are ready to use RenderMan for Blender. See"}
{"id": "fb1a762d343666a69bcdbada4fd6efa5904f304be14cec5e42928559a1ff1b4e", "item_id": "ed3012f531:32", "text": "Getting Started in Blender"}
{"id": "23387c389232ee337dd113ac7da43b4a581158c1f0d20350ca0e7b63dff10434", "item_id": "ed3012f531:33", "text": "to begin using RenderMan for Blender."}
